Manifest contains a map of Class strings, their complete package names and their parent classes.

Constructor

new(?file : String)

Instance Variables

classPackageMap(default,null) : prime.types.SimpleDictionary_String_String

Hash containing references from single class names to their full names including the package. I.e. "Label" => "prime.gui.components.Label"

subClassMap(default,null) : prime.types.SimpleDictionary_String_flash_Vector

Dictionary with lists for each class and its subclasses

superClassMap(default,null) : prime.types.SimpleDictionary_String_String

Hash containing references from classes to their super classes. I.e. "prime.gui.components.Label" => "prime.gui.core.UIDataComponent"
